1.Clone the Repository:
  git clone https://github.com/amansxcalibur/Terminal-Chaos.git
  cd Terminal-Chaos

2.Exploring the Repository
  List Files:
  ls

3.Examine File Contents:
  cat filename

4.Check Repository Status
  git status

5.Git Log:
  git log

6.search files:
  grep 'search_term' filename
  grep -r 'search_term' .

7.list branches:
  git branch

8.list and review tasks:
  git tag
  git show tag_name

9.List All Files Including Hidden Ones:
  ls -a

10.Documentation Review:
   cat README.md
   cat CONTRIBUTING.md

11.Collaboration and Updates:
   git add .
   git commit -m "Describe the changes or findings"
   git push origin branch_name
